5 Section 2. Whereas it is essential to public health that the citizens of the
6 Commonwealth be aware and informed of the safety of liability shield products, an
7 emergency is declared to exist, and this Act takes effect upon its passage and approval by
8 the Governor or upon its otherwise becoming a law.
